            "values": [
                "The radiation code originates from the ECMWF model (older cycle) with a few modifications done in global climate model ECHAM4. These are the additional greenhouse gases, 14.6 \u03bcm band of ozone,  the single scattering properties of cloud droplets and ice crystals are derived from Mie theory, water vapor continuum has temperature weighted band averages of e-type absorption including ratios, and the effective radius of droplets and ice crystals is parameterized in terms of the liquid and ice water content, respectively."
